{"tid":2280880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大媽陪你燒雞翼 | 屯門公園禁止開檔 大媽燒烤場開騷狂收利是","createTime":"2020-11-10T23:30:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T10:47:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcd05ad391b877cb19a42b5d2a5e402e1aad6d6","tid":2280880,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T23:30:16.000Z","msg":"久不久便見屯門公園歌唱大媽的新聞, 因她們能做到鑊鑊新鮮, 鑊鑊高潮, 即使武肺來襲, 她們都能鑽到空子, 來淘阿伯恩客的棺材本。<br />\n<br />\n今年中, 傳媒曾踢爆屯門歌唱大媽違反限聚令, 在屯門公園賣唱, 之後又有新招, 透過以廿蚊至二百蚊不等的價錢來販賣啤酒, 汽水及蒸餾水等, 變相間接收受歌酬賺錢。屯門歌唱大媽的生命力, 真的令人嘆為觀止!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_766037_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_766037_0&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7InHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=f3365b5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_766037_0&h=64f34538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_766037_0</a>"},{"pid":"673857daa290da4618df9292e15820069507268f","tid":2280880,"uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"呢d燒烤場十間有九間都無牌，瘋狂做投訴撚啦"},{"pid":"fc9a246cc9eb53485957a5d80e556a9b6cdebe44","tid":2280880,"uid":63909,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"鑽到空子...<br />\n屌點解佢死都會用呢D 用字"},{"pid":"557dcb26082f3d8476ae4beb37cd60aeaa10b076","tid":2280880,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fc9a246cc9eb53485957a5d80e556a9b6cdebe44","tid":2280880,"uid":63909,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T23:33:27.000Z","msg":"鑽到空子...<br />\n屌點解佢死都會用呢D 用字"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T23:40:03.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bb9328d5fa78a846e2955fe5b248c9221c0bda","tid":2280880,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"557dcb26082f3d8476ae4beb37cd60aeaa10b076","tid":2280880,"uid":51271,"lik